9102329%2Cimgsize-1196304.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fbjp-odisha-vice-president-lekhasri-samantasinghar-resigns-joins-bjd-ahead-of-polls%2Farticleshow%2F109102294.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fridge%2C%20Smart%20TV%20As%20Evidence%20In%20Money%20Laundering%20Case%20Against%20Hemant%20Soren%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EInvoices%20of%20a%20refrigerator%20and%20smart%20TV%20are%20among%20the%20evidence%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20used%20to%20support%20its%20claim%20that%20Jharkhand's%20ex-chief%20minister%20Hemant%20Soren%20acquired%208.86%20acres%20of%20land%20worth%20more%20than%20Rs%2031%20crore%20illegally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20federal%20probe%20agency%20obtained%20these%20receipts%20from%20two%20Ranchi-based%20dealers%20and%20attached%20those%20to%20its%20charge%20sheet%20filed%20against%20the%2048-year-old%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20(JMM)%20leader%20and%20four%20others%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20special%20PMLA%20court%20of%20Judge%20Rajiv%20Ranjan%20in%20Ranchi%20took%20cognisance%20of%20the%20prosecution%20complaint%20on%20April%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Soren%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20ED%20on%20January%2031%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20related%20to%20the%20alleged%20land%20grab%2C%20shortly%20after%20he%20resigned%20as%20chief%20minister.%20He%20is%20currently%20in%20judicial%20custody%20in%20Birsa%20Munda%20jail%20at%20Hotwar%20in%20Ranchi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20ED%2C%20the%20two%20gadgets%20were%20purchased%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20family%20members%20of%20one%20Santosh%20Munda%20who%20told%20the%20agency%20that%20he%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bresiding%20as%20a%20caretaker%20of%20the%20property%20of%20Hemant%20Soren%20on%20the%20said%20land%20(8.86%20acres)%20for%2014%20to%2015%20years%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20used%20Mr%20Munda's%20statement%20to%20counter%20Mr%20Soren's%20claim%20that%20he%20had%20no%20link%20with%20the%20said%20land.%20The%20ED%20also%20rejected%20the%20claim%20of%20a%20person%20named%20Rajkumar%20Pahan%20on%20the%20piece%20of%20land%2C%20alleging%20that%20he%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bfront%26quot%3B%20for%20Soren%20to%20keep%20the%20asset%20under%20his%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20claimed%20that%20soon%20after%20Mr%20Soren%20was%20issued%20the%20first%20summons%20in%20this%20case%20in%20August%20last%20year%2C%20Mr%20Pahan%20wrote%20to%20the%20deputy%20commissioner%20of%20Ranchi%20stating%20he%20and%20some%20others%20have%20the%20land%20in%20possession%20and%20the%20earlier%20mutation%20in%20the%20name%20of%20other%20owners%20be%20cancelled%20and%20they%20may%20be%20saved%20from%20being%20evicted%20from%20their%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20%26quot%3Brestored%26quot%3B%20the%20land%20to%20Mr%20Pahan%20on%20January%2029%2C%20two%20days%20before%20Mr%20Soren's%20arrest%2C%20so%20that%20the%20JMM%20leader's%20control%20and%20possession%20remained%20%26quot%3Bunimpeded%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ED%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20federal%20probe%20agency%2C%20the%20land%20was%20originally%20a%20'Bhuinhari'%20property%20that%20cannot%20be%20transferred%20or%20sold%20to%20anyone%20under%20general%20situations%20and%20'Mundas'%20and%20'Pahans'%20were%20the%20owners%20of%20such%20land%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20immovable%20asset%20was%20later%20sold%20to%20some%20persons%20by%20the%20original%20allottees%20but%20Soren%20got%20them%20%26quot%3Bevicted%26quot%3B%20and%20gained%20control%20of%20the%20land%20in%202010-11%2C%20the%20ED%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESantosh%20Munda%20also%20told%20the%20ED%20that%20Hemant%20Soren%20and%20his%20wife%20Kalpana%20visited%20the%20land%20%26quot%3Btwo%20to%20three%20times%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20he%20worked%20as%20a%20labourer%20when%20a%20boundary%20wall%20was%20being%20erected%20at%20the%20plot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20claims%20Mr%20Munda%20was%20entrusted%20the%20charge%20of%20the%20property's%20caretaker%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20Mr%20Soren%2C%20apart%20from%20another%20accused%20in%20the%20case%20Hilariyas%20Kachhap%20who%20got%20an%20electricity%20meter%20installed%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20refrigerator%20was%20purchased%20in%20February%202017%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Mr%20Munda's%20son%20while%20a%20smart%20TV%20was%20purchased%20in%20November%202022%20in%20the%20name%20of%20his%20daughter%20at%20the%20address%20where%20the%20land%20is%20located%20in%20Ranchi%2C%20the%20agency%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20the%20ED%20said%2C%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bestablished%26quot%3B%20that%20Santosh%20Munda%20and%20his%20family%20were%20residing%20at%20this%20property%20and%20it%20was%20not%20in%20possession%20of%20the%20accused%20person%20Rajkumar%20Pahan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRajkumar%20Pahan%20is%20acting%20as%20a%20frontman%20of%20Hemant%20Soren%20so%20that%20the%20property%20can%20somehow%20be%20shown%20to%20be%20in%20possession%20of%20Pahan%20and%20his%20family%20members%20and%20the%20evidence%20against%20Mr%20Soren%20can%20be%20frustrated%20and%20the%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20can%20be%20kept%20concealed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20agency%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20has%20listed%20these%20two%20bills%20as%20evidence%20and%20attached%20them%20with%20the%20charge%20sheet%20under%20the%20'relied%20upon%20documents'%20category%20as%20it%20sought%20prosecution%20of%20Soren%20and%20others%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Soren%2C%20Rajkumar%20Pahan%2C%20Hilariyas%20Kachhap%2C%20Bhanu%20Pratap%20Prasad%20and%20Binod%20Singh%20have%20been%20named%20as%20accused%20in%20the%20191-page%20charge%20sheet.%20The%20piece%20of%20land%20--%2012%20adjacent%20plots%20guarded%20by%20a%20cemented%20wall%20--%20has%20also%20been%20attached%20by%20the%20ED%20on%20March%2030%20and%20it%20is%20valued%20at%20over%20Rs%2031.07%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20stumbled%20upon%20this%20case%20of%20alleged%20land%20grab%20while%20probing%20another%20money%20laundering%20case%20of%202022%20where%20a%204.55-acre%20land%20of%20the%20defence%20ministry%20at%20Morabadi%20in%20Ranchi%20was%20%26quot%3Bacquired%20fraudulently%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20ED%2C%20the%20probe%20found%20that%20%26quot%3Ba%20group%20of%20some%20private%20persons%20in%20connivance%20with%20government%20officials%20including%20the%20ex-DC%20Ranchi%2C%20Chhavi%20Ranjan%2C%20and%20Bhanu%20Pratap%20Prasad%20(sub-inspector%20of%20Jharkhand%20government%20revenue%20department)%20were%20part%20of%20a%20land-grabbing%20syndicate.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThey%20were%20involved%20in%20corrupt%20practices%20which%20included%20acquiring%20properties%20based%20on%20false%20deeds%2C%20falsification%20of%20government%20records%2C%20tampering%20with%20original%20revenue%20documents%20etc%2C%20to%20facilitate%20private%20persons%20to%20acquire%20landed%20properties%20fraudulently%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712471460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fdam60amo_hemant-soren_625x300_22_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffridge-smart-tv-as-evidence-in-money-laundering-case-against-hemant-soren-5391704%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Invoices%20of%20a%20refrigerator%20and%20smart%20TV%20are%20among%20the%20evidence%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20used%20to%20support%20its%20claim%20that%20Jharkhand's%20ex-chief%20minister%20Hemant%20Soren%20acquired%208.86%20acres%20of