of%20Vythiri%20police%20station%20wrote%20that%20seniors%20and%20peers%20%26quot%3Bphysically%20and%20mentally%20tortured%26quot%3B%20Sidharthan%2C%20driving%20him%20to%20die%20by%20suicide%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20They%20assaulted%20Sidharthan%20on%20February%2016%20from%209%20am%20to%202%20pm%20till%20February%2017%20continuously%20with%20hand%20and%20using%20a%20belt%20and%20subjected%20him%20to%20cruel%20ragging.%20This%20made%20him%20in%20an%20utter%20stage%20of%20mental%20stress%20and%20feeling%20that%20he%20can%20neither%20continue%20study%20in%20the%20Institute%20and%20complete%20this%20course%20nor%20go%20home%20dropping%20the%20course.%20As%20he%20is%20so%20mentally%20stressed%2C%20he%20felt%20that%20there%20is%20no%20option%20for%20him%20other%20than%20suicide%2C%20he%20committed%20suicide%20by%20hanging%20himself%20in%20the%20bathroom%20of%20men's%20hostel%20in%20between%2012.30%20pm%20and%2013.45%20pm%20on%20February%2018%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20report%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20had%20re-registered%20the%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20filed%20with%20Wayanad's%20Vythiri%20police%20station%20against%2020%20people%20on%20Friday%20night%2C%20within%20hours%20of%20getting%20a%20notification%20from%20the%20Centre.%20The%20procedure%20in%20state-referred%20cases%20is%20such%20that%20the%20CBI%20starts%20an%20investigation%20by%20re-registering%20the%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala%20Chief%20Minister%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20had%20assured%20a%20CBI%20probe%20on%20March%209%20after%20a%20political%20uproar%20over%20the%20case.%20The%20issue%20snowballed%20into%20a%20huge%20controversy%20with%20the%20Opposition%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20alleging%20the%20state%20government%20was%20yet%20to%20hand%20over%20key%20files%20to%20the%20CBI%20weeks%20after%20the%20assurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20student's%20family%20hd%20also%20alleged%20the%20state%20government%20deliberately%20tried%20to%20delay%20the%20CBI%20probe%20by%20not%20handing%20them%20over%20files%20and%20destroying%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%2C%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20candidate%20from%20the%20Thiruvananthapuram%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20has%20assured%20the%20student's%20family%20to%20expedite%20the%20CBI%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20student's%20father%2C%20Jayaprakash%2C%20alleged%20his%20son%20had%20been%20harassed%20for%20eight%20months%20before%20his%20death.%20He%20alleged%20SFI%20leaders%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bcamping%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20college%20for%20many%20months%20and%20his%20son%20had%20been%20made%20to%20strip%20and%20sit%20on%20his%20knees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20were%20all%20aware%20of%20what%20was%20going%20on.%20They%20could%20have%20put%20an%20end%20to%20it%20back%20then.%20I%20cannot%20believe%20that%20the%20senior%20SFI%20leaders%20were%20unaware%20of%20what%20was%20happening%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712471340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F1be4btnc_kerala-student_640x480_04_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkerala-news%2Fkerala-student-sidharthan-js-found-dead-in-college-hostel-continuously-assaulted-for-29-hours-report-5391673%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20has%20taken%20over%20the%20case%20into%20the%20death%20of%20a%2020-year-old%20veterinary%20student%20in%20a%20college%20hostel%20in%20Kerala's%20Wayanad%20district.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkerala-news%2Fkerala-student-sidharthan-js-found-dead-in-college-hostel-continuously-assaulted-for-29-hours-report-5391673%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.