2028%2C%20admitted%20on%20Friday%20to%20murdering%20his%20wife%20Holly%20Bramley%2C%2026%2C%20in%20March%20after%20weeks%20of%20denying%20the%20allegations%2C%20even%20joking%20with%20police%20officers%20who%20came%20looking%20for%20her%20that%20she%20%26quot%3Bmight%20be%20hiding%20under%20the%20bed%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%26quot%3BGot%20%C2%A350%20for%20disposing%20of%20a%20body%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMetson%20likely%20stabbed%20his%20wife%20several%20times%20in%20the%20bedroom%20and%20chopped%20the%20body%20in%20the%20bathroom.%20He%20then%20put%20the%20pieces%20in%20plastic%20bags%20and%20stored%20them%20in%20a%20kitchen%20larder%2C%20a%20cold%20area%20for%20storage%20of%20food%2C%20before%20getting%20rid%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlmost%20a%20week%20later%20and%20before%20police%20arrived%20at%20his%20door%2C%20he%20paid%20his%20friend%20%C2%A350%20to%20help%20him%20dispose%20of%20the%20body%20parts.%20%26quot%3BJust%20got%20%C2%A350%20for%20disposing%20of%20a%20body%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20friend%20wrote%20in%20a%20text%20message%2C%20the%20court%20was%20told.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20later%2C%20plastic%20bags%20were%20discovered%20floating%20in%20the%20Witham%20river%20by%20a%20morning%20walker.%20One%20of%20the%20bags%20had%20a%20human%20hand%20and%20another%20Ms%20Bramley%20shaved%20head.%20In%20total%2C%20divers%20found%20224%20body%20parts%20with%20some%20still%20missing.%20The%20body%20was%20chopped%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20it%20was%20impossible%20to%20find%20a%20cause%20of%20death%2C%20the%20court%20was%20told.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%26quot%3BEvil%20monster%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Bramley's%20mother%20told%20the%20court%20that%20her%20daughter%20had%20been%20married%20for%20just%2016%20months%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bevil%20monster%26quot%3B%20didn't%20allow%20her%20to%20meet%20her%20family%20for%20years%20and%20the%20couple%20were%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20separating%20when%20he%20killed%20her%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20murdering%20his%20wife%2C%20he%20searched%20for%20questions%20like%20%26quot%3BWhat%20benefits%20do%20I%20get%20if%20my%20wife%20has%20died%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BCan%20someone%20haunt%20me%20after%20they%20die%3F%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Bramley%20had%20once%20fled%20her%20home%20with%20her%20pet%20rabbits%20and%20sought%20police%20help%20after%20he%20killed%20her%20hamsters%20by%20putting%20them%20in%20a%20food%20blender%20and%20the%20microwave%20oven.%20He%20also%20put%20her%20new%20puppy%20in%20a%20washing%20machine%2C%20only%20for%20Ms%20Bramley%20to%20find%20the%20dead%20animal%20spinning%20inside%20the%20machine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EGruesome%20murder%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2024%2C%20Lincolnshire%20Police%20reached%20the%20couple's%20home%20for%20a%20welfare%20check%20on%20Ms%20Bramley%20after%20receiving%20distress%20reports.%20When%20Metson%20answered%20the%20door%2C%20he%20claimed%20he%20was%20a%20victim%20of%20domestic%20abuse%20by%20his%20wife%20and%20showed%20the%20policemen%20a%20bite%20mark%20on%20his%20arm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20wound%20occurred%20when%20Ms%20Bramley%20tried%20to%20free%20herself%20from%20her%20husband%20as%20she%20was%20killed%20a%20few%20days%20earlier%2C%20a%20UK%20court%20was%20told.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolicemen%20also%20found%20blood-soaked%20sheets%20in%20the%20bathtub%2C%20several%20dark%20sports%20on%20the%20floor%20and%20a%20strong%20smell%20of%20ammonia%20and%20bleach%20throughout%20the%20house.%20Metson%20later%20told%20police%20his%20wife%20had%20left%20with%20a%20women's%20support%20group%20a%20few%20days%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20killer%2C%20who%20is%20to%20be%20sentenced%20on%20Monday%2C%20has%20not%20revealed%20how%20and%20why%20he%20killed%20his%20wife.%20His%20lawyer%2C%20however%2C%20claimed%20that%20his%20diagnosis%20of%20an%20autism%20spectrum%20disorder%20was%20a%20factor%20in%20the%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712470860000%2C%22v