%20in%20touch%20with%20snake%20charmers%20now%20in%20jail.%20Police%20have%20also%20explained%20the%20grounds%20for%20invoking%20sections%20of%20Narcotic%20Drugs%20and%20Psychotropic%20Substances%20Act%2C%201985%20against%20the%20YouTuber.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20police%20officer%20Vidya%20Sagar%20Mishra%20said%20the%20venom%20seized%20from%20the%20snake%20charmers%20belongs%20to%20krait%20snakes%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20cobra%20family.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20filed%20a%20chargesheet%20against%20all%20named%20accused.%20We%20have%20also%20included%20statements%20by%20an%20adequate%20number%20of%20witnesses.%20This%20includes%20an%20expert%20from%20Mumbai's%20Department%20of%20Forensic%20Medicine%20and%20Toxicology.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%20last%20year%2C%20five%20snake%20charmers%20were%20arrested%20from%20a%20banquet%20hall%20in%20Noida's%20Sector%2051%20and%20nine%20snakes%2C%20five%20of%20them%20cobra%2C%20were%20recovered%20from%20them.%20About%2020%20ml%20of%20suspected%20snake%20venom%20was%20also%20found.%20The%20snake%20charmers%20were%20arrested%20and%20are%20now%20out%20on%20bail.%20The%20investigation%20into%20the%20matter%20led%20the%20cops%20to%20Elvish%20Yadav%20and%20the%20other%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712468640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F5b8jgu58_elvish-yadav-gets-bail-in-snake-venom-case-deets-inside_625x300_22_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felvish-yadav-how-elvish-yadav-got-venom-to-parties-how-elvish-yadav-got-venom-to-parties-shocking-allegations-in-chargesheet-5391519%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22YouTuber%20Elvish%20Yadav%20used%20a%20virtual%20phone%20number%20to%20coordinate%20the%20supply%20of%20snake%20venom%20for%20rave%20parties%20and%20send%20instructions%20to%20snake%20charmers%2C%20Noida%20police%20has%20said%20in%20its%201%2C200-page%20chargesheet%20filed%20in%20an%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20court%20yesterday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felvish-yadav-how-elvish-yadav-got-venom-to-parties-how-elvish-yadav-got-venom-to-parties-shocking-allegations-in-chargesheet-5391519%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felvish-yadav-how-elvish-yadav-got-venom-to-parties-how-elvish-yadav-got-venom-to-parties-shocking-allegations-in-chargesheet-5391519%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felvish-yadav-how-elvish-yadav-got-venom-to-parties-how-elvish-yadav-got-venom-to-parties-shocking-allegations-in-chargesheet-5391519%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20Fighting%20For%20Political%20Survival%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20campaign%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20gathers%20momentum%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20the%20leaders%20of%20two%20prominent%20regional%20parties%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20are%20fighting%20a%20battle%20for%20political%20survival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20polls%20are%20also%20an%20acid%20test%20for%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20and%20his%20deputy%20and%20NCP%20chief%20Ajit%20Pawar%20as%20they%20have%20cast%20their%20lots%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20by%20splitting%20their%20respective%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20challenge%20is%20tougher%20for%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar%20as%20they%20are%20out%20of%20power%20and%20have%20lost%20control%20of%20their%20parties%20--%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%2C%20respectively%20--%20along%20with%20the%20original%20name%20and%20electoral%20symbol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20and%20the%20Maharashtra%20assembly%20speaker%20have%20recognised%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar-led%20NCP%20and%20Shinde-led%20Sena%20as%20the%20real%20NCP%20and%20the%20real%20Shiv%20Sena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20journalist%20and%20political%20analyst%20Prakash%20Akolkar%20told%20PTI%20that%20both%20the%20leaders%20need%20to%20put%20up%20an%20impressive%20performance%20in%20the%20polls%2C%20or%20else%20they%20risk%20political%20extinction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUddhav%20Thackeray%20needs%20to%20get%20at%20least%20six%20to%20seven%20MPs%20elected%20to%20keep%20his%20flock%20together%20till%20the%20assembly%20polls%20which%20are%20due%20later%20this%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Akolkar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thackeray%20had%20to%20contest%20as%20many%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20as%20his%20party%20contested%20when%20he%20was%20a%20BJP%20ally%20in%202019%2C%20and%20he%20is%20doing%20just%20that%2C%20declaring%2021%20candidates%20so%20far%20notwithstanding%20the%20Congress%20staking%20claim%20to%20some%20of%20these%20seats%2C%20the%20senior%20journalist%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCP%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar)%20is%20contesting%2010%20seats%20as%20per%20the%20seat-sharing%20formula%20worked%20out%20with%20his%20MVA%20allies%20Sena%20(UBT)%20and%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Akolkar%20said%20the%20key%20seat%20for%20Pawar%20senior%20is%20his%20home%20turf%20Baramati%2C%20where%20his%20daughter%20and%20three-time%20MP%20Supriya%20Sule%20is%20facing%20a%20challenge%20from%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20wife%20Sunetra%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Sharad%20Pawar%20loses%20Baramati%2C%20everything%20is%20lost%20for%20him.%20This%20is%20a%20battle%20between%20him%20and%20his%20nephew%20Ajit%20who%20has%20managed%20and%20controlled%20Baramati%20constituency%20for%20the%20family%20all%20these%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Akolkar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%2083%2C%20has%20never%20lost%20an%20election%20in%20his%20political%20career%20spanning%20more%20than%20five%20decades%2C%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20has%20never%20contested%20a%20direct%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20became%20chief%20minister%2C%20Mr%20Thackeray%20was%20elected%20to%20the%20legislative%20council.%20The%20Shinde%20faction%20often%20taunts%20him%20for%20not%20stepping%20out%20of%20house%20when%20he%20held%20the%20top%20post%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20elections%2C%20Mr%20Thackeray%20has%20been%20travelling%20to%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20state%2C%20and%20his%20rallies%20are%20getting%20good%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharad%20Pawar%2C%20too%2C%20is%20on%20the%20move%20while%20also%20reaching%20out%20to%20his%20old%20rivals%20in%20Pune%20district%20(where%20Baramati%20constituency%20is%20located)%20like%20the%20Thopates%20of%20Congress%20to%20ensure%20his%20daughter%20has%20a%20smooth%20sailing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20MVA's%20seat-sharing%20talks%20with%20Dalit%20leader%20Prakash%20Ambedkar's%20Vanchit%20Bahujan%20Aghadi%20(VBA)%20falling%20through%2C%20the%20direct%20contest%20between%20the%20MVA%20and%20Mahayuti%20alliance%20has%20become%20a%20triangular%20fight%2C%20and%20in%20Akolkar's%20opinion%20it%20would%20benefit%20the%20ruling%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhay%20Deshpande%2C%20another%20senior%20journalist%2C%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20elections%20will%20also%20test%20the%20claim%20of%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20that%20the%20traditional%20voters%20and%20cadres%20of%20their%20respective%20parties%20are%20loyal%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20unrest%20in%20BJP%20cadres%2C%20and%20it%20will%20have%20to%20be%20seen%20if%20they%20work%20wholeheartedly%20for%20candidates%20of%20Ajit%20Pawar-led%20NCP%20and%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20Deshpande%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Splits%20in%20political%20parties%20is%20not%20a%20new%20phenomenon.%20But%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20rebels%20have%20hijacked%20the%20original%20parties%20after%20the%20split%20and%20got%20recognition%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20slogan%20of%20400-plus%20seats%20is%20meant%20to%20motivate%20BJP%20workers.%20But%20to%20realise%20that%20goal%2C%20the%20BJP%20will%20have%20to%20retain%20the%202019%20tally%20of%2041%20seats%20(which%20it%20won%20in%20alliance%20with%20undivided%20Sena)%20in%20Maharashtra.%20Due%20to%20the%20alignment%20and%20realignment%20of%20political%20equations%2C%20this%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20challenge%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Deshpande%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarshal%20Pradhan%2C%20a%20former%20journalist%20and%20now%20a%20close%20associate%20of%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20claimed%20these%20elections%20are%20really%20about%20the%20survival%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20used%20central%20probe%20agencies%20to%20weaken%20and%20intimidate%20opposition%20parties%2C%20and%20its%20modus%20operandi%20is%20to%20accuse%20opposition%20leaders%20of%20corruption%20and%20then%20induct%20them%20into%20the%20party%20fold%2C%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20was%20in%20power%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20for%20two-and-a-half%20years%2C%20he%20worked%20to%20mitigate%20the%20damage%20caused%20by%20cyclones%20in%20Konkan%20and%20save%20lives%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20Mr%20Pradhan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUddhav%20Thackeray's%20growing%20political%20stature%20during%20this%20period%20made%20the%20BJP%20insecure%2C%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClyde%20Crasto%2C%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20NCP%20(SP)%2C%20echoed%20the%20same%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20election%20is%20a%20battle%20for%20survival%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20because%20they%20are%20afraid%20they%20will%20lose%2C%20and%20therefore%20resorting%20to%20cheap%20tactics%20like%20breaking%20up%20parties%20and%20families%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERatnakar%20Mahajan%2C%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20and%20political%20commentator%2C%20said%2C%26quot%3B%20Both%20Shinde%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar%20are%20past%2060.%20To%20start%20a%20new%20innings%20at%20this%20age%20is%20not%20easy.%20But%20they%20did%20this%20(split%20their%20parties)%20not%20for%20power%20but%20to%20avoid%20possible%20action%20by%20the%20ED%2C%20Income%20Tax%20and%20CBI%20which%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20using%20to%20harass%20opposition%20leaders.%26quot%3B%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20will%20be%20looking%20for%20vindication%20of%20their%20political%20stands%20in%20these%20elections%2C%20he%20opined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20the%202019%20assembly%20elections%2C%20an%20unusual%20alliance%20emerged%20through%20the%20initiative%20of%20these%20leaders.%20There%20was%20dissension%20within%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20about%20joining%20hands%20with%20Pawar.%20But%20the%20two%20leaders%20went%20ahead%20and%20Thackeray%20became%20the%20chief%20minister.%20Now%20they%20are%20fighting%20to%20retain%20their%20hold%20over%20voters%20in%20the%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712468520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fmsieg6lg_sharad-pawar-uddhav-thackeray_625x300_25_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsharad-pawar-uddhav-thackeray-fighting-for-political-survival-5390983%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20the%20leaders%20of%20two%20prominent%20regional%20parties%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20are%20fighting%20a%20battle%20for%20political%20survival.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsharad-pawar-uddhav-thackeray-fighting-for-political-survival-5390983%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsharad-pawar-uddhav-thackeray-fighting-for-political-survival-5390983%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsharad-pawar-uddhav-thackeray-fighting-for-political-survival-5390983%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A