%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109099983.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EPakistan's%20Foreign%20Minister%20Ishaq%20Dar%20is%20set%20to%20visit%20China%20following%20safety%20concerns%20for%20Chinese%20firms%20post%20the%20recent%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20terrorist%20attack%20that%20claimed%205%20Chinese%20engineers'%20lives.%20The%20attack%20not%20only%20brought%20the%20project%20to%20a%20standstill%20but%20also%20sparked%20concerns%20among%20international%20businesses%20over%20the%20safety%20of%20their%20employees%20in%20the%20area.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-minister-likely-to-visit-china-to-quell-bomb-blast-after-effects%2Farticleshow%2F109099983.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-minister-likely-to-visit-china-to-quell-bomb-blast-after-effects%2Famp_articleshow%2F109099983.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-minister-likely-to-visit-china-to-quell-bomb-blast-after-effects%2Famp_articleshow%2F109099983.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Influencer%20Ravindra%20Balu%20Bharti%20Ordered%20To%20Pay%20Rs%2012%20Crore.%20Here's%20Why%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMarket%20regulator%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20has%20asked%20a%20financial%20influencer%20(finfluencer)%20to%20return%20unlawfully%20obtained%20gains%20amounting%20to%20over%20Rs%2012%20crore.%20This%20comes%20as%20a%20significant%20move%20to%20safeguard%20investor%20interests%20and%20uphold%20market%20integrity%20amidst%20growing%20concerns%20about%20fraudulent%20practices%20in%20the%20securities%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20finfluencer%20in%20question%2C%20identified%20as%20Ravindra%20Balu%20Bharti%2C%20has%20been%20instructed%20by%20SEBI%20to%20deposit%20the%20Rs%2012%20crore%20into%20an%20interest-bearing%20Escrow%20Account%20held%20in%20a%20nationalised%20bank.%20The%20creation%20of%20this%20Escrow%20Account%20serves%20to%20secure%20the%20funds%20under%20SEBI's%20jurisdiction%2C%20ensuring%20they%20cannot%20be%20released%20without%20explicit%20permission%20from%20the%20regulatory%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavindra%20Balu%20Bharti%20is%20the%20founder%20of%20Ravindra%20Bharti%20Education%20Institute%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%20(RBEIPL)%2C%20a%20company%20he%20co-founded%20in%202016%20alongside%20his%20wife%2C%20Shubhangi%20Bharti.%20RBEIPL%20reportedly%20engages%20in%20educational%20activities%20related%20to%20stock%20market%20trading%2C%20operating%20through%20a%20website%20titled%20%26quot%3BBharti%20Share%20Market%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESEBI's%20interim%20order%20extends%20beyond%20Ravindra%20Balu%20Bharti%20alone.%20The%20regulator's%20order%20encompasses%20RBEIPL%20and%20several%20other%20individuals%20associated%20with%20the%20entity.%20Notably%2C%20SEBI%20has%20barred%20them%20from%20offering%20investment%20advisory%20services%20or%20engaging%20in%20securities%20trading%20activities%20until%20further%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESEBI's%20investigation%20exposed%20a%20pattern%20of%20misconduct%20wherein%20investors%20were%20misled%20with%20promises%20of%20exorbitant%20returns%2C%20reaching%20up%20to%201000%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia's%20capital%20market%20in%20the%20recent%20times%20has%20witnessed%20tremendous%20growth%2C%20characterised%20particularly%20by%20increasing%20participation%20of%20the%20common%20public%20based%20on%20investors'%20confidence.%20This%20confidence%20in%20the%20capital%20market%20can%20be%20sustained%20largely%20by%20ensuring%20investors%20protection.%20Disclosure%20and%20transparency%20are%20the%20two%20pillars%20on%20which%20market%20integrity%20rests%2C%26quot%3B%20SEBI's%20order%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestors%20who%20chose%20these%20services%20had%20to%20engage%20in%20an%20agreement%20that%20outlined%20the%20specific%20terms%20and%20conditions%20for%20receiving%20investment%20advice.%20This%20agreement%20detailed%20the%20fees%20associated%20with%20accessing%20advisory%20services%2C%20projected%20investment%20returns%2C%20and%20the%20percentage%20of%20profits%20to%20be%20shared%20if%20returns%20surpass%20expectations.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712466240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fk2q3kid_ravindra-bharti_625x300_07_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finfluencer-ravindra-balu-bharti-ordered-to-pay-rs-12-crore-heres-why-5391403%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Market%20regulator%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20has%20asked%20a%20financial%20influencer%20(finfluencer)%20to%20return%20unlawfully%20obtained%20gains%20amounting%20to%20over%20Rs%2012%20crore.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finfluencer-ravindra-balu-bharti-ordered-to-pay-rs-12-crore-heres-why-5391403%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finfluencer-ravindra-balu-bharti-ordered-to-pay-rs-12-crore-heres-why-5391403%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finfluencer-ravindra-balu-bharti-ordered-to-pay-rs-12-crore-heres-why-5391403%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mcap%20of%204%20of%20top-10%20firms%20hit%20Rs%201.71%20trn%3B%20HDFC%20Bank%2C%20LIC%20lead%20gainers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712466170000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-04%2F04%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1712171991-0233.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fmcap-of-4-of-top-10-firms-hit-rs-1-7