2%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWill%20Be%20Able%20To%20Answer%20That%20After...%26quot%3B%3A%20Ganguly%20On%20Pant's%20T20%20WC%20Selection%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20India%20skipper%20Sourav%20Ganguly%20said%20on%20Saturday%20that%20Rishabh%20Pant%20is%20%26quot%3Bfully%20fit%26quot%3B%20but%20added%20that%20the%20wicketkeeper-batter%20should%20be%20given%20some%20more%20time%20to%20prepare%20himself%20for%20India%20team%20selection%20for%20the%20upcoming%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%20the%20West%20Indies%20and%20USA.%20Pant%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Capitals%20skipper%20seems%20to%20be%20hitting%20his%20strides%20in%20the%20ongoing%20IPL%20with%20consecutive%20half-centuries%20after%20returning%20to%20professional%20cricket%20following%20a%20harrowing%20car%20crash%20in%20December%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20he%20thinks%20Pant%20is%20ready%20for%20selection%20in%20the%20India%20squad%2C%20Ganguly%2C%20who%20is%20DC's%20director%20of%20cricket%2C%20said%20after%20a%20team%20training%20session%20that%3A%20%26quot%3BLet%20a%20few%20more%20matches%20go.%20He%20is%20doing%20very%20well.%20As%20you%20all%20must%20have%20seen%2C%20you%20know%2C%20(wicket)%20keeping%2C%20batting.%20He%20has%20held%20up%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20form%20has%20been%20fantastic%2C%20especially%20the%20way%20he%20has%20batted%20in%20the%20last%20two%20games.%20Let%20another%20week%20go%2C%20and%20I'll%20be%20able%20to%20answer%20that%20question...%20provided%20the%20selectors%20want%20to%20pick%20him%20--%20that's%20most%20important.%20He's%20fit%2C%20fully%20fit%2C%26quot%3B%20Ganguly%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPant%20is%20currently%20the%20fourth-highest%20run-getter%20in%20IPL%202024%2C%20having%20scored%20152%20runs%20in%20four%20matches%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20nearly%20160.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDC%20will%20take%20on%20the%20embattled%20five-time%20IPL%20champions%20Mumbai%20Indians%20at%20the%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGanguly%20added%20that%20he%20was%20satisfied%20with%20the%20bowling%20department%20but%20the%20team%2C%20which%20has%20lost%20three%20of%20its%20four%20matches%20so%20far%20this%20season%2C%20could%20do%20with%20an%20extra%20batter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20used%20the%20bowling%20part%20of%20it%20well%20in%20terms%20of%20Mukesh%20(Kumar)%2C%20who's%20developed%20under%20Delhi%20Capitals%2C%20Khaleel%20(Ahmed)%20and%20Ishant%20(Sharma).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrithvi%20Shaw...%20he's%20come%20back%20into%20good%20form%20this%20season.%20Obviously%2C%20Rishabh%20is%20a%20domestic%20Indian%20talent.%20Abhishek%20Porel%20has%20started%20out%20well%20this%20season.%20We%20need%20to%20find%20one%20more%20batsman%20who%20can%20do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legendary%20cricketer%20added%20that%20the%20likes%20of%20young%20players%20such%20as%20Ricky%20Bhui%2C%20and%20Kumar%20Kushagra%20could%20get%20opportunities%20to%20play%20as%20the%20tournament%20progresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYoung%20Jharkhand%20batter%20Kushagra%20was%20bought%20by%20DC%20for%20a%20mindboggling%20Rs%207.2%20crore%20in%20the%20IPL%20auction%20but%20is%20yet%20to%20play%20an%20IPL%20match%20this%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20about%20opportunities%20at%20this%20level.%20Hopefully%20with%20the%20young%20players%20like%20(Ricky)%20Bhui%2C%20(Kumar)%20Kushagra%2C%20we%20can%20give%20them%20opportunities%20and%20see%20how%20it%20goes.%20It's%20also%20on%20the%20balance%20of%20the%20side%2C%20whether%20you%20want%20to%20go%20the%20bowling%20way%20or%20the%20batting%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ganguly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20he%20(Kushagra)%20will%20play.%20We're%20looking%20for%20an%20opportunity%20for%20him%20to%20play.%20We%20saw%20(Sameer)%20Rizvi%20play%20for%20Chennai%2C%20he%20also%20got%20a%20very%20high%20price%20tag.%26quot%3B%20The%20stylish%20former%20batter%20felt%20that%20Indian%20talent%20will%20flourish%20in%20the%20IPL%20as%20it%20is%20getting%20lots%20of%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20Indian%20talent%20who's%20doing%20well%20in%20IPL.%20(We)%20saw%20(Riyan)%20Parag%20do%20well%20for%20Rajasthan%20so%20far.%20Then%20there%20is%20Punjab%20(Kings')%20Shashank%20Singh%2C%20he%20did%20well%20in%20the%20last%20game.%20Prabhsimran%20is%20also%20doing%20well%20for%20Punjab%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20young%20talents%20around%20in%20the%20IPL%20and%20that's%20the%20way%20it%20has%20been%20over%20a%20period%20of%20time.%20It's%20a%20platform%20for%20young%20talent%20to%20come%20and%20play%20well.%20And%2C%20the%20more%20opportunities%20they%20are%20given%2C%20they%20will%20play%20well%20as%20the%20tournament%20progresses.%26quot%3B%20Ganguly%20does%20not%20want%20to%20read%20too%20much%20into%20Mumbai%20Indians'%20dismal%20performance%20so%20far.%20The%20five-time%20champions%20have%20lost%20all%20three%20games%20so%20far%20this%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMumbai%20is%20a%20good%20side.%20We%20are%20a%20good%20team%20as%20well.%20We%20won%20one%20game%20against%20Chennai.%20We%20expect%20Mumbai%20to%20play%20well%20because%20they've%20been%20a%20great%20franchise%20over%20a%20long%20period%20of%20time.%20They%20have%20some%20quality%20players%20in%20the%20squad%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20T20%20is%20such%20a%20format%20that%20sometimes%20you%20get%20into%20this%20situation%20where%20you%20lose%20a%20couple%20of%20games%20(or)%20three%20games%20and%20then%20you%20have%20to%20find%20a%20way%20to%20get%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20Ganguly%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKuldeep%20Yadav%20to%20undergo%20fitness%20test%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGanguly%20said%20wrist%20spinner%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20will%20undergo%20a%20fitness%20test%20to%20determine%20his%20availability%20for%20the%20match%20against%20MI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe'll%20undergo%20a%20fitness%20test%20today.%20He%20has%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20groin%20stiffness%20(and)%20that's%20why%20he%20missed%20the%20last%20two%20games.%20By%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20we'll%20get%20to%20know%20whether%20he's%20available%20tomorrow%20or%20not%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ganguly%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGanguly%20added%20that%20DC%20will%20also%20have%20to%20look%20for%20a%20replacement%20for%20Mitchell%20Marsh%2C%20who%20got%20injured%20while%20playing%20against%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712465640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fj9j35c8g_rishabh-pant-bcci_625x300_03_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fwill-be-able-to-answer-that-after-sourav-ganguly-on-rishabh-pants-t20-world-cup-selection-5387713%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rishabh%20Pant%20is%20currently%20the%20fourth-highest%20run-getter%20in%20IPL%202024%2C%20having%20scored%20152%20runs%20in%20four%20matches%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20nearly%20160.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20conducts%20military%20exercises%20in%20contested%20South%20China%20Sea%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712465456000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109100780%2Cimgsize-956500.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchina-conducts-military-exercises-in-contested-south-china-sea%2Farticleshow%2F109100590.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China's%20military%20conducted%20'combat%20patrols'%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%2C%20coinciding%20with%20joint%20drills%20by%20the%20Philippines%2C%20US%2C%20J