gana's%20Rangrareddy%20district%20yesterday%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20your%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20(K%20Chandrashekar%20Rao)%20did%20here%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20the%20BJP%20is%20doing%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20has%20become%20Extortion%20Directorate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi's%20remarks%20on%20the%20central%20agency%20are%20part%20of%20the%20Opposition's%20charge%20at%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20misusing%20probe%20agencies%20for%20political%20objectives.%20Leaders%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Centre%20on%20this%20issue%20during%20a%20rally%20at%20Delhi's%20Ramlila%20Maidan%20after%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20KCR-led%20BRS%20government%20is%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20massive%20controversy%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20allegations%20that%20senior%20police%20officers%20tapped%20the%20phones%20of%20Opposition%20leaders%2C%20including%20current%20Chief%20Minister%20Revanth%20Reddy%2C%20and%20several%20celebrities%20and%20businessmen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20senior%20police%20officers%20have%20been%20arrested%20after%20Mr%20Reddy%20ordered%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20matter.%20It%20is%20also%20alleged%20that%20surveillance%20of%20businessmen%20was%20used%20to%20blackmail%20them%20into%20contributing%20to%20the%20BRS%20party%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20have%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20BRS%20as%20the%20shocking%20allegations%20come%20to%20the%20fore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20minister%20and%20KCR's%20son%20KT%20Rama%20Rao%20has%20suggested%20that%20if%20any%20phone-tapping%20occurred%2C%20it%20may%20have%20been%20limited%20to%20a%20few%20troublemakers%20or%20criminals.%20The%20Congress%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20%26quot%3Bexaggerating%20it%20as%20an%20international%20scam%26quot%3B%2C%20he%2