20Got%20BJP%20Ticket%20Due%20To%20Women's%20Quota%20Bill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20public%20address%2C%20actor%20Kangana%20Ranaut%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.boomlive.in%2Ffact-check%2Fkangana-ranaut-himachal-pradesh-mandi-bjp-candidate-womens-reservation-bill-fact-check-24816%5C%22%3Eclaimed%20that%20she%20received%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party's%20(BJP)%20ticket%20to%20contest%20elections%20from%20the%20Mandi%20constituency%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20because%20of%20the%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBOOM%20found%20that%20the%20claim%20was%20false%20since%20the%20bill%20has%20not%20been%20brought%20into%20effect%20yet.%20On%20March%2024%2C%202024%2C%20the%20BJP%20announced%20Kangana%20Ranaut%20as%20the%20party's%20candidate%20to%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20from%20Himachal%20Pradesh's%20Mandi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20abide%20by%20the%20high%20command's%20decision%20on%20contesting%20Loksabha%20polls%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20on%20X%20while%20adding%20that%20she%20looks%20forward%20to%20being%20a%20%26quot%3Bworthy%20Karyakarta%20and%20a%20reliable%20public%20servant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20recent%20public%20address%20in%20Mandi's%20Balh%20village%2C%20Ranaut%20spoke%20about%20how%20she%20was%20granted%20the%20BJP%20ticket%20due%20to%20the%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%2C%20that%20grants%2030%25%20reservation%20to%20women%20(in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha)%20is%20the%20reason%20why%20I%20have%20this%20stage%20today.%20Because%20of%20that%2C%20your%20daughter%20from%20Mandi%20has%20this%20stage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClick%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC5RJoT5R9ou%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20view%20the%20video%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fperma.cc%2FRT4P-DU7L%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20an%20archive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFACT%20CHECK%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBOOM%20found%20that%20the%20claims%20are%20false%20and%20the%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20has%20not%20been%20implemented%20yet%20and%20will%20not%20be%20done%20so%20at%20least%20until%202029.%20The%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20Nari%20Shakti%20Vandan%20Adhiniyam%2C%20seeks%20to%20reserve%20one-third%20of%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20legislative%20state%20assemblies%20for%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20was%20passed%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20September%2020%2C%202023%2C%2027%20years%20after%20it%20was%20first%20introduced%20in%20the%20parliament.%20On%20September%2022%2C%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20too%2C%20passed%20the%20Bill%20unanimously.%20Having%20been%20passed%20in%20both%20houses%20of%20the%20parliament%2C%20the%20bill%20now%20needed%20the%20President's%20assent%2C%20which%20was%20given%20on%20September%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20meant%20that%20the%20bill%20fulfilled%20all%20requirements%20to%20become%20a%20law.%20However%2C%20this%20bill%20would%20be%20brought%20into%20effect%20only%20after%20the%20census%20and%20delimitation%20exercises%20were%20complete.%20A%20delimitation%20exercise%20involves%20allotting%20the%20number%20of%20seats%20as%20well%20as%20boundaries%20of%20territorial%20constituencies%20across%20the%20country%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20elections.%20This%20exercise%20is%20set%20to%20take%20place%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20census%20released%20after%202026.%20The%20centre%20has%20not%20yet%20concluded%20the%202021%20census%20due%20to%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20essentially%20means%20that%20the%20bill%20will%20come%20into%20effect%20after%20the%20delimitation%20exercise%2C%20which%20will%20in%20turn%20begin%20after%20the%20release%20of%20the%20latest%20census.%20While%20speaking%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20September%2020%2C%202023%2C%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20that%20the%20delimitation%20exercise%20would%20be%20conducted%20only%20after%20the%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20and%20it%20would%20be%20at%20least%20until%202029%20that%20the%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20is%20implemented.%20Several%20opposition%20leaders%20at%20the%20time%20had%20criticised%20this%20method%20used%20to%20implement%20the%20Women's%20Reservation%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%20leader%20Atishi%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20have%20the%20provisions%20of%20delimitation%20and%20Census%20been%20included%3F%20This%20means%20that%20women's%20reservation%20won't%20be%20implemented%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20We%20demand%20that%20the%20provisions%20of%20delimitation%20and%20Census%20be%20done%20away%20with%20and%20the%20women's%20reservation%20be%20implemented%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(DMK)%20leader%20Kanimozhi%20had%20said%20that%20the%20reservation%20could%20be%20easily%20extended%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20%26quot%3BStop%20this%20tokenism.%20This%20bill%20is%20called%20Nari%20Shakti%20Vandhan%20Bill.%20Stop%20saluting%20us.%20We%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20saluted%2C%20put%20on%20a%20pedestal%2C%20or%20worshipped.%20We%20want%20to%20be%20respected%20as%20equals%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(This%20story%20was%20originally%20published%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.boomlive.in%2Ffact-check%2Fkangana-ranaut-himachal-pradesh-mandi-bjp-candidate-womens-reservation-bill-fact-check-24816%5C%22%3EBOOM%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20republished%20by%20NDTV%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Shakti%20Collective.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712462340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F3b23bg5_kangana-ranaut-_625x300_07_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffact-check-kangana-ranaut-falsely-claims-she-got-bjp-ticket-due-to-womens-quot