%20TikTok%2C%20Lil%20Maqueta%20has%20promoted%20brands%20as%20big%20as%20BMW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20was%20to%20%26quot%3Bcreate%20something%20never%20seen%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20German%20premium%20carmaker%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAttracting%20a%20younger%2C%20technology-savvy%20generation%20is%20for%20us%20the%20icing%20on%20the%20cake%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaud%20Lejeune%2C%20who%20heads%20up%20the%20Paris-based%20digital%20strategy%20agency%20AD%20Crew%2C%20said%20that%20it%20isn't%20difficult%20for%20the%20public%20to%20accept%20AI%20influencers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20actors%20on%20TV%3A%20we%20know%20it%20isn't%20real%20yet%20we%20follow%20them%20and%20we%20find%20it%20interesting%2C%20it's%20like%20watching%20a%20mini-series.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAD%20Crew%20represents%20more%20than%2030%20influencers%2C%20but%20Lejeune%20created%20her%20own%20virtual%20influencer%2C%20Metagaya%2C%20two%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20current%20level%20of%20design%20didn't%20exist%20then.%20It's%20technical%2C%20you've%20got%20to%20dress%20them%2C%20take%20photos%20for%20the%20background%2C%20create%20a%20story%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lejeune%2C%20acknowledging%20that%20Metagaya%20didn't%20turn%20out%20very%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rapid%20technological%20progress%20brought%20by%20the%20likes%20of%20OpenAI's%20Sora%20video%20generator%20could%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20create%20and%20operate%20realistic%20virtual%20influencers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDeepfakes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHuman%20influencers%20are%20also%20seizing%20on%20AI%20technology%20to%20make%20better%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrance's%20Charles%20Sterlings%20sees%20an%20opportunity%20to%20improve%20translations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20uses%20different%20tools%20on%20platforms%20like%20HeyGen%20and%20Rask.ai%20to%20automatically%20translat