%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20started%20Health%20Sutra%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20true%20enough%2C%20even%20the%20Indian%20government%20designated%20it%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9CYear%20of%20Millets%E2%80%9D.%20The%20company%20sells%20cereal%20flakes%20such%20as%20Jowar%20Flakes%2C%20Ragi%20Flakes%2C%20and%20Barley%20Flakes%2C%20as%20well%20as%20seven%20different%20types%20of%20%3Cem%3Erava%20%3C%2Fem%3Efor%20%3Cem%3Eidli%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Eupma%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20biscuits%20made%20from%20ragi%20and%20jowar.%20The%20brand%20has%20clocked%20an%20impressive%20annual%20revenue%20of%20Rs%202.5%20crores%20since%20its%20inception.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-9-1705584781.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sai%20created%20Health%20Sutra%20to%20bring%20millet%20alternatives%20to%20the%20market.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Health%20Sutra.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-9-1705584781.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-9-1705584781-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-9-1705584781-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-9-1705584781-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-9-1705584781-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338561%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESai%20created%20Health%20Sutra%20to%20bring%20millet%20alternatives%20to%20the%20market.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Health%20Sutra.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Unlocking%20the%20power%20of%