0our%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337937%2Fbest-budget-homestay-in-uttarakhand-the-nanda-stone-mukteshwar-by-ashish-verma%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheart%20was%20in%20the%20mountains.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20yearning%20to%20go%20back%20home%20only%20became%20stronger%20with%20time.%20We%20decided%20to%20plan%20our%20move%20back%20home%20and%20start%20Himalaica%2C%E2%80%9D%20Varun%20said%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENestled%20between%20forests%20and%20streams%2C%20at%20a%20small%20distance%20from%20the%20hustle%20and%20bustle%20of%20Nainital%20city%2C%20Himalaica%20is%20a%20perfect%20getaway%20to%20experience%20the%20Himalayas%20with%20delicious%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EVarun%20and%20Ite%E2%80%99s%20Homecoming%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDubbing%20themselves%20the%20%E2%80%98Himalayan%20boy%20and%20girl%E2%80%99%2C%20Varun%20and%20Ite%2C%20who%20spent%20their%20formative%20years%20in%20Nainital%20and%20Srinagar%2C%20share%20an%20immense%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F98569%2Fdyo-organic-village-resort-uttarakhand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elove%20for%20nature%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20the%20wilderness.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20retreat%20became%20a%20pivotal%20point%20in%20bringing%20the%20two%20back%20home.%20%E2%80%9CMaking%20the%20move%20back%20after%20dedicating%20so%20many%20years%20of%20our%20careers%20abroad%20was%20a%20significant%20decision.%20However%2C%20it%20all%20began%20when%20we%20first%20laid%20eyes%20on%20the%20land%20where%20Himalaica%20stands%20today.%20We%20devote%20the%20majority%20of%20our%20time%20in%20India%20to%20collaborating%20with%20our%20chefs%20and%20caretakers%2C%20striving%20to%20provide%20the%20best%20service%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Ite%20.%3C%2Fp